hkust-menu/collapse.description:
whether the menu is collapsed (available only in vertical mode), default: false.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/background-color.description:
background color of Menu (hex format), default: #ffffff.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/text-color.description:
text color of Menu (hex format), default: #303133.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/active-text-color.description:
text color of currently active menu item (hex format), default: #409EFF.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/default-openeds.description:
array that contains indexes of currently active sub-menus

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/unique-opened.description:
whether only one sub-menu can be active, default: false.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/menu-trigger.description:
how sub-menus are triggered, only works when `mode` is 'horizontal', default: hover.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/router.description:
whether `vue-router` mode is activated. If true, index will be used as 'path' to activate the route action, default: false.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/collapse-transition.description:
whether to enable the collapse transition, default: true.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-attributes)

hkust-menu/select.description:
callback function when menu is activated

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-events)

hkust-menu-item/click.description:
callback function when menu-item is clicked

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#menu-item-events)

hkust-submenu/popper-class.description:
custom class name for the popup menu

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#submenu-attributes)

hkust-submenu/show-timeout.description:
timeout before showing a sub-menu, default: 300.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#submenu-attributes)

hkust-submenu/hide-timeout.description:
timeout before hiding a sub-menu, default: 300.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#submenu-attributes)

hkust-submenu/disabled.description:
whether the sub-menu is disabled, default: false.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#submenu-attributes)

hkust-submenu/popper-append-to-body.description:
whether to append the popup menu to body. If the positioning of the menu is wrong, you can try setting this prop, default: level one Submenu: true / other Submenus: false.

[Docs](https://gitee.com/x_c_huang/hkust-ui.git/#/en-US/component/menu#submenu-attributes)
